Bitmap: 
Average(R+G+B) < PPMMax/2, if less than, output 0, if greater than, output 1

Grayscale:
Average(R+G+B) / (PPMMax*PGMMax)

Sepia:
see spec

Mirror:
reflect the left half onto the right half

Thumbnail:
shrink image by scaling factor

N_up:
tile image X times


implementation details:
1. implement image allocation/deallocation routines
2. implement function for each transformation
* read, output struct, for each input pixel, update respoective output pixel based on mode, write output, destroy all allocated memory
3. call appropriate transformation function from main()